@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #F5F5F5
  BorderColor #555555
}
rectangle "secret small numbers\n(the key, kept private)" as S
rectangle "big public grid" as G
rectangle "a little fuzz" as F
rectangle "PUBLIC PADLOCK\n(safe to show everyone)" as P #E8F0FE
S --> P : multiply, then add fuzz\n(easy, one direction)
G --> P
F --> P
P ..> S : un-fuzz back to the key?\nBLOCKED, too hard even for a quantum robot
@enduml
